tags.charge: £1 for an hour, £3 a day, £10 for minibuses, blue badge holders free
tags.description: In January 2023 Forestry and Land Scotland will be introducing car park charging in Faskally Wood. The car parking charge will be £1 for an hour and £3 for all day, the minibus charge will be £10 all day. Blue badge holders park free of charge.
